        "data": "<h2>Bug</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix Jenkins pipeline lock</li>\n<li>Fix Ingress error which some times is not created after CI is deleted and re-created</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Improvements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Alert the user about duplicated environment keys</li>\n<li>CLI opts in CI expanded to accept a predefined list of args</li>\n</ul>"
